How to run
    - make
    - ./tetris

This is a tetris game written in C++ using ncurses.

The game is played using WASD keys.
- A and D move the tetrimino left and right
- W rotates the tetrimino
- S increases the speed of the tetrimino

The goal of the game is to clear as many lines as possible and get a high score
before the tetriminos reach the top of the board.

Try and beat my high score of 5600!

You get 100 points for every line you clear.